## 7. Performance and Optimization
Profile and optimize based on data.

@performance_rules [
  {
    "id": "guidelines",
    "rule": "Profile before optimizing; use appropriate data structures, minimize allocations.",
    "severity": "high",
    "example": "Use std::vector for dynamic arrays."
  },
  {
    "id": "memory",
    "rule": "Apply RAII, use smart pointers, avoid leaks.",
